      • cycleIndicatedSuggestionForward

        public boolean cycleIndicatedSuggestionForward()
        Select the next indicated suggestion.
        Returns:
        true if a change occurred. False otherwise.

        This may return false if the only suggestion is already selected, or if no suggestions are available.

      • cycleIndicatedSuggestionBackward

        public boolean cycleIndicatedSuggestionBackward()
        Select the previous indication suggestion.
        Returns:
        true if a change occurred. False otherwise.

        This may return false if the only suggestion is already selected, or if no suggestions are available.
